HEADWORD: Wording
<hw>Word"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or manner of expressing in
words; style of expression; phrasing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It is believed this <qex>wording</qex> was above his known
style.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wordish</ent>⟦br⟧
